data.description: Welcome to 2910 Church Hill! This 1,948-square-foot residence is nestled in the charming Wedgwood Subdivision offering a picturesque backdrop to Wedgwood Park. Boasting 4 generously sized bedrooms, including a master suite with full bath. The eat-in kitchen is equipped with sturdy oak cabinets, a gas stove, and refrigerator that stays with the home. The adjacent hearth room features peg and plank flooring, complemented by a cozy wood-burning fireplace. Throughout the home, you'll find a harmonious blend of peg and plank floors, some carpeting, and elegant six-panel doors. The expansive family room is a standout feature, showcasing cedar beams, vaulted ceiling, a brick accent wall, and a wall of windows that bathe the space in natural light. A sliding glass door leads to the shaded deck, providing a perfect spot to unwind while enjoying the great view of the park.  This home is being sold "AS IS," inviting you to make it your own, add your personal touch and create lasting memories.
